OL,5, Netflix is to broadcast its first Welsh
OL,6, language drama.                        
OL,8,FThe streaming giant said it hoped it   
OL,9,Fcould play a role in helping to        
OL,10,F"promote and preserve the Welsh        
OL,11,Flanguage".                             
OL,13,FIt has bought the licence for S4C's Dal
OL,14,Fy Mellt, a gritty crime thriller which 
OL,15,Fwill air from April 2023.              
OL,17,FSet in Cardiff, Soho, Porthmadog and   
OL,18,FHolyhead, it follows a group of misfits
OL,19,Fas they come together to pull off a    
OL,20,Fheist.                                 
